outokumpu to close nickel refineri dure summer the finnish metal and mine group outokumpu oy said it will close it nickel refineri at harjavalta in central finland for six week in juli and august thi year due to current low price on the nickel market . `` we consid nickel price as bad at the moment , although they have been rise slightli sinc januari , '' refineri sale manag pekka purra said . he said the closur will mean a drop in product of 3,000 tonn in 1987 from last year 's output of 17,800 tonn . the closur wa also a move to cut labour cost as no extra staff have to be employ dure holiday to keep the plant open .